#Patient Monitoring System

## Description
This project consists of a **frontend built with HTML** and a **backend powered by Flask**.  
It allows users to:
- Register
-Login
-Add Patient and get patient details
-record heart rate and display patient heart rate

## How to Run the Project
Follow these steps to run the project locally:

1. Run the backend Flask application
python app.py

2. Open your web browser and search
http://127.0.0.1:5000

